&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( kannada : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ; english : guts ) is a 2012 indian kannada crime drama film directed by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; kittur , based on the novel of the same name written by agni shridhar . it stars aditya in the lead role . atul kulkarni , achyuth kumar , srujan lokesh , dharma and &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; mansukhani feature in supporting roles . the film is based on the real-life incidents that occurred in the 1990s and is about cult figures in the karnataka underworld such as sridhar , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; rai and bachchan . the film opened to widespread critical acclaim upon theatrical release . it won the special jury award at the 6th bangalore international film festival .